div1.p: UNITED STATES OF AMERICA, Western District of Washington } ss:

I hereby certify and return that I served the annexed Writ of Habeas Corpus on the therein-named Henry M. White, Commissioner of Immigration by handing to and leaving a true and correct copy thereof with Henry M. White at Seattle, Wash in said District on the 18th day of February, A.D. 1915
IN THE DISTRICT COURT OF THE UNITED STATES FOR THE WESTERN DISTRICT OF WASHINGTON NORTHERN DIVISION
IN THE MATTER OF THE APPLICATION OF GUSSIE GOLDMAN WOODS, ETC. FOR A WRIT OF HABEAS CORPUS
FILED IN THE U.S. District Court, Western Dist. of Washington, NORTHERN DIVISION, FEB 19 1915 FRANK L. CROSBY, Clerk, By EML Deputy
